OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FWest Ham's final-day win over Leeds
OL,8,Fwas too little too late as they
OL,9,Fslumped to relegation from the Premier
OL,10,FLeague.
OL,12,FThe Hammers needed a victory and for
OL,13,FTottenham to lose at home to Everton
OL,14,Fto stay up and send Spurs down instead.
OL,16,FThey kept their side of the bargain as
OL,17,Fsecond-half goals from Taty
OL,18,FCastellanos, Jarrod Bowen and Callum
OL,19,FWilson sank Leeds 3-0.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FBut Spurs, who had very sportingly
OL,8,Fbeen bad enough to take the relegation
OL,9,Fscrap to the last day, beat Everton to
OL,10,Fsurvive by two points.
OL,12,FIt brought to an end West Ham's 15-
OL,13,Fyear stay in the top flight, with
OL,14,Frelegation coming a decade after the
OL,15,Fcontroversial move to the London
OL,16,FStadium and hollow promises from the
OL,17,Fowners that came with it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FTheir brief revival under Nuno
OL,8,FEspirito Santo, who replaced Graham
OL,9,FPotter as manager in September, began
OL,10,Ftoo late and fizzled out too early.
OL,12,F"We sold our soul, for this ****hole"
OL,13,Frang around the former Olympic Stadium
OL,14,Fas fans turned their anger towards
OL,15,Fchairman David Sullivan.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
