OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FThe Leeds fans were in no mood to be
OL,8,Fsympathetic, chanting "Millwall away
OL,9,Fole ole", a fixture which could keep
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police busy next
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FRelegation will come as no surprise to
OL,14,Fseasoned West Ham watchers, with the
OL,15,Fclub having been in decline ever since
OL,16,FDavid Moyes took them to Conference
OL,17,FLeague glory in 2023.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
