OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FSupporters will point to the sale of
OL,8,FDeclan Rice to Arsenal and subsequent
OL,9,Fdismal investment of his #105 million
OL,10,Ftransfer fee.
OL,12,FWest Ham cherry-picked cheap players
OL,13,Ffrom relegated clubs; James Ward-
OL,14,FProwse, Kyle Walker-Peters and Mateus
OL,15,FFernandes from Southampton, Crysencio
OL,16,FSummerville from Leeds and Mads
OL,17,FHermansen from Leicester.
OL,19,FNow, the same will happen to them,
OL,20,Fwith Bowen, Summerville and Fernandes
OL,21,Flikely first out of the door.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FThe signs proclaiming 'end-of-season
OL,8,Fsale, 50% off' on the giant screens at
OL,9,Fthe ground felt distinctly portentous.
OL,11,FAs for the match, Leeds almost sucked
OL,12,Fthe hope out of the building in the
OL,13,Fopening moments when James Justin
OL,14,Fshanked a shot across goal, but Lukas
OL,15,FNmecha was unable to divert the ball
OL,16,Fhome.
OL,18,FNmecha then jinked his way into the
OL,19,FWest Ham penalty area and squared for
OL,20,FDominic Calvert-Lewin, but Hermansen
OL,21,Fcame out to make a vital block.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FThe Hammers found some momentum and
OL,8,FPablo Felipe's goalbound shot was
OL,9,Fheaded over by Pascal Struijk while
OL,10,FFernandes saw a drive beaten away by
OL,11,FKarl Darlow.
OL,13,FThen, two minutes before half-time,
OL,14,Fthe news filtered through that Joao
OL,15,FPalhinha had put Spurs ahead, and the
OL,16,Fenergy was sapped out of the home
OL,17,Fcrowd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779711071
OL,3,CWest Ham relegated as 3-0 win over
OL,4,CLeeds is not enough to overhaul
OL,5,CTottenham
OL,7,FPablo, the Portuguese striker signed
OL,8,Fin January for #21 million who
OL,9,Fcontributed no goals, was replaced at
OL,10,Fthe break by Callum Wilson.
OL,12,FSome hope arrived in the 67th minute
OL,13,Fwhen Bowen swung in a corner and
OL,14,FCastellanos rose highest at the far
OL,15,Fpost to bury a powerful header.
OL,17,FWilson struck the third in stoppage
OL,18,Ftime shortly after Fernandes had sent
OL,19,FBowen scampering through, with the
OL,20,FHammers captain at least able to say a
OL,21,Flikely farewell with a goal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
